PN,37601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FThe partner of a school caretaker who
OL,8,Fwas stabbed to death by paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane in
OL,10,FNottingham, has told an inquiry it
OL,11,Ffelt like her partner had been "killed
OL,12,Ftwice" - because she was first told he
OL,13,Fhad died in a car crash.
OL,15,FIan Coates, 65, died after being
OL,16,Fstabbed just over an hour after 19-
OL,17,Fyear-old undergraduates Barnaby Webber
OL,18,Fand Grace O'Malley-Kumar were killed
OL,19,Fin the early hours of June 13 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMr Coates' partner, Elaine Newton,
OL,8,Ftold the public inquiry into the
OL,9,FNottingham attacks that she was first
OL,10,Ftold by police that Mr Coates had died
OL,11,Fin a road traffic accident.
OL,13,FMs Newton told the hearing of her
OL,14,Finitial denial that it could be Mr
OL,15,FCoates, believing he was at work, and
OL,16,Fthat it took more than four hours
OL,17,Fbefore she was told the truth about
OL,18,Fhow her partner had actually died.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FShe said: "They said he was in an RTA,
OL,8,Fa road accident. I said 'He will be at
OL,9,Fwork, it's not Ian'. They said 'No,
OL,10,Fit's an RTA'. I said 'Did he crash
OL,11,Finto anyone? What happened?'
OL,13,F"They said 'We can't tell you'. I said
OL,14,F'Is anyone else hurt?' and they said
OL,15,F'We can't tell you'. That's all they
OL,16,Fwere telling me for about five hours."
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMs Newton said two young police
OL,8,Fofficers, a male and a female, spent
OL,9,Fthe morning with her after she was
OL,10,Ftold Mr Coates had died but neither of
OL,11,Fthem could give her any more
OL,12,Finformation about what had happened.
OL,14,FShe said the female officer kept going
OL,15,Foutside to speak to someone, adding:
OL,16,F"She kept saying there's no
OL,17,Finformation, there's no information.
OL,18,FShe couldn't tell me anything for all
OL,19,Fthose hours."
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FShe told the inquiry that police
OL,8,Fliaison officers later asked her to
OL,9,Ftell them what she knew about what had
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,F"And I said 'Yes, Ian was in an RTA
OL,13,Fbut I don't know any more than that',"
OL,14,FMs Newton said.
OL,16,F"And they looked shocked on their
OL,17,Ffaces and said 'You've got the wrong
OL,18,Finformation, You've been told the
OL,19,Fwrong information. Ian's been killed
OL,20,Fand he's been stabbed'. That's how I
OL,21,Flearned."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@fO]xD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FAsked how it felt to be told how he
OL,8,Fhad really died, Ms Newton said: "It
OL,9,Ffelt like he'd been killed twice. It
OL,10,Fwasn't right.
OL,12,F"The first information, I accepted,
OL,13,Fbut the second I couldn't accept. You
OL,14,Fdon't know which one was true, or have
OL,15,Fthey got the wrong person. It was not
OL,16,Fright, it was a mess."
OL,26,@pD@bOUtD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMs Newton said she had told
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police that she did
OL,9,Fnot want to see the face of Calocane `
OL,10,Fwho is being referred to during the
OL,11,Finquiry as VC ` but was later shown
OL,12,Fvideos of him walking around the city
OL,13,Fon the morning of the attacks.
OL,15,FShe said: "I didn't want to see VC's
OL,16,Fface, I didn't want him to take my
OL,17,Flife over as much as he has done. I
OL,18,Fwanted to keep his face out of my
OL,19,Fmind."
OL,26,@wD@KOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMs Newton also said she only became
OL,8,Faware of previous incidents involving
OL,9,FCalocane and the police during the
OL,10,Finquiry process.
OL,12,FShe said: "I was never told any
OL,13,Finformation about his past... The
OL,14,Ffirst time was this hearing, I didn't
OL,15,Fknow anything about any of this at
OL,16,Fall."
OL,26,@tD@KOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FDuring a meeting with the now-retired
OL,8,Fchief constable of Nottinghamshire
OL,9,FPolice Kate Meynell, Ms Newton said
OL,10,Fshe was not told about Calocane's past
OL,11,Finvolvement with police but was
OL,12,Finstead told about a WhatsApp group in
OL,13,Fwhich police officers had discussed
OL,14,Fthe fatal attacks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FAsked what she would have done had she
OL,8,Fhad known this information, Ms Newton
OL,9,Fsaid: "I wouldn't have thanked Kate
OL,10,FMeynell for all the information she
OL,11,Fgave me and for letting me come and
OL,12,Fvisit her. I have lost faith in the
OL,13,Fpolice and I feel like I have not been
OL,14,Fgiven the information and have been
OL,15,Flied to really.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,F"I should have been given information
OL,8,Fabout his past, not straight away, but
OL,9,Fdown the line. She could have given me
OL,10,Fmore information when I went, rather
OL,11,Fthan just telling me about the
OL,12,FWhatsApp group."
OL,14,FIn the wake of the attacks, Ms Newton
OL,15,Fasked Nottinghamshire Police how
OL,16,FCalocane was allowed to be "roaming"
OL,17,Fthe city so long after he had carried
OL,18,Fout the fatal stabbings and was given
OL,19,F"excuses".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@PO]xD@\OUxD@dO]{D@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FShe said: "I did ask that question to
OL,8,FKate Meynell and (my family liaison
OL,9,Fofficer) and they said it could be
OL,10,Fquite a few reasons, there was not
OL,11,Fenough police that morning, Nottingham
OL,12,Fis a big place.
OL,14,F"Those were the excuses I got. I did
OL,15,Fsay it was early in the morning and
OL,16,Fthere wouldn't have been a lot of
OL,17,Fpeople around. They said they might
OL,18,Fjust not have had enough police
OL,19,Fofficers in that morning."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMs Newton told the inquiry she was
OL,8,F"glad this has all come out" but added
OL,9,Fthat "the police need to be more
OL,10,Fhelpful".
OL,12,FShe said the prosecution of Calocane
OL,13,Fwas not explained clearly enough,
OL,14,Fadding: "I mean meeting or you're
OL,15,Fintroduced to people, you never, you
OL,16,Fdon't actually understand because its
OL,17,Frushed, it's not explained enough,
OL,18,Fthey think you understand because it's
OL,19,Ftheir job.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@\O]qD@FOUrD@HO]vD@IOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,F"The way they talk about the criminal
OL,8,Fjustice... you don't understand it."
OL,10,FCalocane was discharged by
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust (NHFT) in September
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FMs Newton read an email she sent to
OL,16,FNHFT following meetings with
OL,17,Frepresentatives from the trust.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FShe read her email to the inquiry,
OL,8,Fwhich said: "I want you to understand
OL,9,Fthat I am not interested in apologies
OL,10,Fbecause it is too late, too little."
OL,12,FIn the email, she said she holds the
OL,13,FNHS responsible for the deaths of Mr
OL,14,FCoates, Mr Webber and Ms O'Malley-
OL,15,FKumar.
OL,17,F"I have zero confidence in any changes
OL,18,Fthat NHS makes in the future. It does
OL,19,Fnot learn its lessons and does not
OL,20,Fcare about people, only statistics and
OL,21,Fnumbers," she wrote.
OL,26,@pD@MOUrD@dO]yD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,F"I believe that is how you see Ian
OL,8,FCoates, as just another statistic that
OL,9,Fyou brush aside and file away.
OL,11,F"What I want is the individuals
OL,12,Fresponsible for the catastrophic NHS
OL,13,Ffailings to be held to account."
OL,15,FShe added: "I want those who failed to
OL,16,Fmanage VC's care to be struck off from
OL,17,Fever being in a position of care ever
OL,18,Fagain."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@`O]wD@LOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1774444274
OL,3,CPartner of caretaker killed by Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane 'was told he died in car
OL,5,Ccrash'
OL,7,FMs Newton told the inquiry: "I think
OL,8,Fthe police have let the public and
OL,9,Fmyself and all other families down."
OL,11,FAsked why, she said: "Because they
OL,12,Fdidn't do their job properly, they
OL,13,Fdidn't communicate with the NHS, the
OL,14,FNHS didn't communicate with the police.
OL,16,F"So I think between them all they've
OL,17,Fcaused this."
OL,26,@oD@]OUqD@dO]sD@VOUxD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
